Scripts to promote Lightwave to a Domain Controller. 
vmdird built with --enable-winjoin just be installed.

Result: Windows clients can domain join to
        this promoted Lightwave Domain Controller


Usage: lightwave-promote-dc.sh [[IP_PSC]  [Admin PWD]]
IP_PSC    : IP of Photon Instance to promote as a Domain Controller
Admin PWD : Administrator password

Both of these values can be set as variables:
    LIGHTWAVE_AD
    ADMIN_PASSWORD
